article_title: HealthSource RI’s individual clients must renew policies for 2015
article_text:
HealthSource RI’s individual clients must renew policies for 2015

The 26,000-plus people who signed up for insurance through Rhode Island’s health exchange will have to sign up again if they want to remain insured next year, and those who do will find new plans, new...
